      "title": "Curfew for Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A gazette notice has been issued imposing curfew for the Colombo district from 12.00 noon today (14) to 5.00 am tomorrow (15).",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has issued this gazette announcement as the Acting President."
